“All I Want For Christmas Is You” by Mariah Carey Vintage “Andrews Sisters” style cover by Postmodern Jukebox ft. Tatum Langley, Lauren De Marco, Kyndle Wylde.
PMJ World Tour Tix: http://pmjtour.com | Get The Song: http://pmjlive.com/alliwant 
Subscribe: http://bit.ly/subPMJ | PMJ on Spotify: http://pmjlive.com/pmjspotify 

The 2025 PMJ video Christmas card is here! Enjoy our 1940s vocal trio take on Mariah Carey’s holiday classic, starring PMJ retro sweethearts Tatum Langley, Lauren De Marco and Kyndle Wylde. Merry Christmas from all of us at Postmodern Jukebox - keep warm & stay vintage!
